{"tid":967344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日我幫老豆interview左一個見工既ive仔","createTime":"2019-01-03T12:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T12:19:31.000Z","uid":1369,"like":5,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6927030ca41d8560d15845d25c0dd47bd43392d","tid":967344,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"之前都in過幾個大學生 <br />\n有上進心，有禮貌 <br />\n我心中都開13-15K比佢地 <br />\n<br />\n但今日有個ive仔大熱天時著全套黑西裝來見室外推銷 <br />\n同佢吹兩咀英文又唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又話好有誠意 <br />\n比我串左幾野 <br />\n之後我問佢有乜理由大學生要求人工15k <br />\n佢又學人要求15k <br />\n<br />\nChok佢幾下 <br />\n跟住佢自已開價8k <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIve仔真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我都會比機會佢 <br />\n因為已經請左兩個大學生 <br />\n兩個都有$15800一個月（加佣） <br />\n再用8k請個ive仔做佢地助手 <br />\n<br />\n等大學生努力跑數幫我老豆賺錢錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e911558764d1f0a040194fc2f98f3f74505384a9","tid":967344,"uid":54754,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"今日大熱天？<br />\n0 分重作"},{"pid":"f2dffac79b036e8eeb5d66b8bb5d19349860581b","tid":967344,"uid":1369,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e911558764d1f0a040194fc2f98f3f74505384a9","tid":967344,"uid":54754,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"今日大熱天？<br />\n0 分重作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"DLLM"},{"pid":"26d4d8aac8227fea4a400a17ce06a348da9c84e7","tid":967344,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"見好多ive仔 Candidate<br />\n<br />\n真係浪費時間<br />\n<br />\n從此改左policy 唔請ive仔<br />\n<br />\n請人ad都加左 bachelor degree or above is a must<br />\n<br />\n但ive仔唔識字<br />\n<br />\n照掉cv來<br />\n<br />\n浪費時間，浪費地球資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390527a573f23c2220ce65cd507623af5ffe78c1","tid":967344,"uid":216817,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:14:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"202462ec631c17dacd95c74e0bb2eb0114875fd0","tid":967344,"uid":25603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"我有個學生同你講野一L樣<br />\n不過佢弱智嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129b4636db0e5ac1b0b0183a5d57c194b4030736","tid":967344,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202462ec631c17dacd95c74e0bb2eb0114875fd0","tid":967344,"uid":25603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"我有個學生同你講野一L樣<br />\n不過佢弱智嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"你係ive仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93b98660b345e5fdc3181f0f450a257f1148208","tid":967344,"uid":25603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"129b4636db0e5ac1b0b0183a5d57c194b4030736","tid":967344,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"202462ec631c17dacd95c74e0bb2eb0114875fd0","tid":967344,"uid":25603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"我有個學生同你講野一L樣<br />\n不過佢弱智嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"你係ive仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T12:19:31.000Z","msg":"Ching 你係咪有讀寫障礙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}